Wholesale Requirements

Minimum Order: $100.00 (All Account Types) Attention All Resellers: Request Qualified Reseller Pricing For Your Online Account TODAY! How To Get Qualified
Welcome to Henry Brandt & Company's online wholesale storefront! We appreciate the opportunity to help you increase your profit margins by purchasing top quality, name brand inspirational closeout merchandise at a fraction of the regular wholesale price!Qualified Reseller Pricing is available for activation to resellers that hold a sales tax identification number and/or are sales tax exempt in the state in which they are located. Generally, two forms of Resale documentation, such as a copy of your retail license and a resale certificate appropriate for your state is required to be on file prior to the activation of Qualified Reseller Pricing. Restrictions and area exclusions may apply. Please see the requirements below for details! 

Questions? Please don't hesitate to give us a call at (417) 334-0988 or email anita@henrybrandt.com!
    ALL Reseller Accounts:How to Pre-Register and Request Activation of Qualified Reseller Pricing in 3 Easy Steps: 

Step 1: Pre-register your business and createa unique log in for your account. The registration form will ask youfor basic information about you and your business.  Be sure to choose one of the Reseller Options offered on the form: New Account or Existing Account at Henry Brandt & Company.Important Note: Registration does not activate Qualified Reseller Pricing!
Step 2: New Reseller Accounts: Please contactus either by phone (417-334-0988) or by email ( anita@henrybrandt.com ) ifyou wish to qualify your business for reseller price activation.  If calling, please note that our regular business hours are Monday-Friday, 8:00 am - 4:00 pm, CST. Restrictions and area exclusions may apply.Existing Reseller Accounts: If you have purchased from Henry Brandt & Company in the past, we will check to ensure that the documents we have on file for your company are current. It is possible that some documents may be out of date. If so, we will request updates via email. 
Step 3: Qualified Reseller Pricing for your online account will be activated when all documents have been received and/or verified, whichever is applicable. Get Started Today!Click Here to Pre-Register









