The Christian Philosophy of Patrick Henry$15.00The Christian Philosophy of Patrick Henry
 
By James M. Wells
Edited by Carris J. Kocher
 
Undoubtedly, this book will serve as an inspiration to every true patriot and defender of freedom’s cause. Almost prophetic in its nature, it will educate you and challenge you toward those pure doctrines of liberty which Patrick Henry held so sacred and dear-doctrines that are so fundamental and vital to our freedom and preservation as a nation, under God. This writing has both strengthened my faith afresh and stirred my convictions anew. It is a ‘must read’ for those who, like Patrick Henry, would seek   ‘preserve us a nation’.
 
